file2sharepoint (0.2.0) stable; urgency=medium

  * Fix glob/file_get_contents return-value checks with proper stderr output
  * Catch \Throwable instead of Exception in upload error handler
  * Fix STDERR: use STDERR constant instead of fopen php://stderr
  * Fix debian/autoload.php: remove double-dollar variable-variable bug
  * Fix debian/rules: correct sed pattern ../vendor (was ../../vendor)
  * Fix bin/file2sharepoint: quote "$@" to preserve arguments with spaces
  * Fix .php-cs-fixer.dist.php: correct package name (was CSas Statement Tools)
  * Add OFFICE365_SITE to .env.example
  * Fix README: remove non-existent OFFICE365_SECRET, rename OFFICE365_PATH
    to SHAREPOINT_LIBRARY, fix typo yourcomapny -> yourcompany
  * Update multiflexi/file2sharepoint.app.json: remove stale OFFICE365_SECRET
    and OFFICE365_PATH vars, add SHAREPOINT_LIBRARY, remove copy-pasted
    RESULT_FILE/ZABBIX_KEY fields, fix APP_DEBUG required/defval, add Czech
    translations, regroup categories
  * Rename WARP.md to AGENTS.md
  * Add phpunit.xml.dist and initial test suite

